# Soul Contract
[color=#2a2a2a]                        [head=2][color=#c96dbf]VOID-BINDING CONTRACT[/color][/head][/color]
─────────────────────────────────────────

I, [color=#7a0000]SAMPLE NAME[/color], henceforth known as the [bold]Seller[/bold], do hereby surrender all claims to my soul(s), voice, and echo to the [bold]Buyer[/bold]: [color=#c96dbf][bolditalic]The Endless Void[/bolditalic][/color].  

Upon signing, the Seller agrees that their essence shall be carried into the [color=#c96dbf][bold]Silence of the Void[/bold][/color], to be observed, absorbed, or ignored at the discretion of [color=#c96dbf][bolditalic]The Void[/bolditalic][/color].  

In exchange, the [bold]Buyer[/bold] shall grant the following Boons, acknowledged as the [italic]Asking Price[/italic]:  

[color=#c96dbf]Boon 1 – Acknowledgement and Certainty of the Voids Gaze[/color]  
‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾  
[color=#c96dbf]Boon 2 – Comfort in Eternal Patience[/color]  
‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾  
[color=#c96dbf]Boon 3 – Protection From Uninvited Whispers[/color]  
‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾  

[color=#aaaaaa][italic]Disclaimer:
By signing this contract, the Seller acknowledges that all posthumous rights, afterlife appeals, and claims of “misfiled souls” are null. The Silence of the Void is binding,  and no insurance covers disturbances therein.[/italic][/color]
